<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَقَامَ رَبِّهِ}</span> ... القِيَامَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْ رَبِّهِ لِلْحِسَابِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَيَّانَ مُرْسَاهَا}</span> ... مَتَى وَقْتُ حُلُولِهَا؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكْرَاهَا}</span> ... لَيْسَ عِنْدَكَ عِلْمُهَا؛ حَتَّى تَذْكُرَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَشِيَّةً}</span> ... مَا بَيْنَ الظُّهْرِ إِلَى غُرُوبِ الشَّمْسِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضُحَاهَا}</span> ... مَا بَيْنَ طُلُوعِ الشَّمْسِ إِلَى نِصْفِ النَّهَارِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>